"What is the ratio of total funding granted to projects with a status of 'completed' versus projects with a status of 'not started' between 2021-09-01 and 2022-09-01 (inclusive)? For each funding record, the project's status is determined by its most recent report dated on or before the date that funding was granted. A project whose status changes within the period may contribute amounts to both categories. Express the answer as a single decimal number rounded to 2 decimal places (completed_total / not_started_total)."
